nodes.text: Fuzzum Squadron was a Z-95 Headhunter squadron in the navy of the Dimok government. During the late Sepan Civil War, they joined forces with the Ripoblus fleet to attack the Imperial Navy forces, which were transferring new TIE/ad starfighters from the Ton-Falk-class escort carrier Tropsobor to the Victory I-class Star Destroyer Protector. Despite their efforts, the squadron was defeated by the Empire.
